1. *Stepenice* su bile staro i izgrebane. (The stairs were old and worn out.)
2. Ona je dosadila do vrha *stepenica*. (She climbed all the way up the stairs.)
3. On je nagazio na *stepenicu*. (He stumbled on the stair.)
4. Ona je lutala po *stepenicama*. (She was wandering through the stairs.)
5. Stigli smo do *stepenica*. (We arrived to the stairs.)
6. Oni su se penjali po *stepenicama*. (They were climbing up the stairs.)
7. Ona je isla niz *stepenice*. (She was going down the stairs.)
8. On je slomio *stepenicu*. (He broke the stair.)